            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>sausage meat</strong> (remove the paper if required!) to a bowl and break it up with a wooden spoon</p><p>Peel and dice your<strong> brown</strong> <strong>onion[s]</strong></p><p>Top, tail and chop your<strong> carrot[s] </strong>into batons</p><p>Chop your <strong>potatoes</strong> (skins on) into bite-sized pieces</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1660647708163-x200.jpg",
