        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add <strong>half</strong> the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>to the sausage meat with <strong>half</strong> the <strong>diced onion </strong>and a generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Mix well until everything is combined, shape into 3 <strong>stuffing balls</strong> per person,<strong> </strong>then transfer to a <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined baking tray (or two!) with the <strong>chopped potatoes</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong>, then put the tray[s] in the oven for 25-30 min or until the stuffing is cooked through and the potatoes are crisp – this is your <strong>sausage stuffing </strong>and <strong>roasties</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1660647714383-x200.jpg",
