    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice the <strong>roasted pork belly</strong> into strips with a sharp knife</p><p>Serve the <strong>roasted pork belly slices </strong>with the <strong>roasties</strong>, <strong>sausage stuffing </strong>and <strong>cooked veg </strong>to the side</p><p>Pour over the <strong>fig gravy</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
